TxtContent:
###Turkish. Clothing

Onlar takım elbise giyerler. They wear suits.

O bir şapka takar.
Q: Is there a difference between "takmak" and "giymek"?
A: Yes. Giymek is for clothing. Takmak is for accessories like hats, scarves, earrings, etc.
